- [ ] Review Slack tasks
- [ ] Review email tasks

## TODO.

- [ ]

## Log.

## Shutting down.

- [ ] Kill work apps
- [ ] Close work tabs
- [ ] Complete day log
- [ ] Look for any observations
- [ ] Update project notes
- [ ] Prepare for tomorrow
- [ ] Clean desk

## Shutdown notes.

- **2 wins:**
	-
	-
- **2 lessons:**
	-
	-
"""

